3.2 Data Types (1 byte = 8 bits)
    a. byte    1 byte
    b. short   2 byte
    c. int     4 byte
    d. float   4 byte
    e. double  8 byte
    f. char    2 byte
    g. long    8 byte
    h. boolean 1 bits

3.3 Naming Convention

    a. camelCase
       Example: myVariableName

    b. snake_case
       Example: my_variable_name

    c. Kebab-case
       Example: my-variable-name

    d. Keep a Good and Short Name
       Example: age, firstName, isMarried

3.4 Keywords
    Only used by language we can't use it as a class name
